# tldr-lint

> Lint and format `tldr` pages
> More information: https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr-lint

- Lint all pages:

`tldr-lint {directory value: pages}`

- Format a specific page to stdout:

`tldr-lint --format {string value: page.md}`

- Format all pages in place:

`tldr-lint --format --in-place {directory value: pages}`
